@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container-fluid my-3">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="mb-4">
                <h1 class="mb-3"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill me-2"></i>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
                <p>At ChatterBox, we are committed to protecting the privacy and security of our users. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-4 g-3">
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-3">
                            <h2 class="card-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-person-fill me-2"></i>User Information</h2>
                            <p class="card-text">When you create an account with ChatterBox, we collect the following information:</p>
                            <ul class="mb-0">
                                <li>Username</li>
                                <li>Email address</li>
                                <li>Password (securely hashed)</li>
                                <li>Birthday</li>
                                <li>User status and last seen information</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-3">
                            <h2 class="card-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-chat-dots-fill me-2"></i>Message Data</h2>
                            <p class="card-text">All messages sent and received through the ChatterBox application are stored in our secure database. This data is necessary for us to provide you with a history of your conversations and enable features like read receipts.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-3">
                            <h2 class="card-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-people-fill me-2"></i>Group Chat</h2>
                            <p class="card-text">If you choose to participate in group chats, we will store the group information, including the group name, members, and messages. This data is necessary for us to provide the group chat functionality.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-3">
                            <h2 class="card-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-fill me-2"></i>File Uploads</h2>
                            <p class="card-text">ChatterBox allows you to share files with your contacts and group members. Any files you upload will be stored on our secure servers, and we will maintain a record of the file metadata, such as the file name, size, and type.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-3">
                            <h2 class="card-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-bell-fill me-2"></i>Notifications</h2>
                            <p class="card-text">ChatterBox may send you notifications, such as message alerts and group invitations. We will store information about these notifications, including the notification type, content, and timestamp.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-3">
                            <h2 class="card-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-search me-2"></i>User Search</h2>
                            <p class="card-text">The user search feature of ChatterBox allows you to find other users by their username or email address. We will store information about your search queries and results to improve the search experience.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-3">
                            <h2 class="card-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-lock-fill me-2"></i>Data Security</h2>
                            <p class="card-text">ChatterBox takes the security of your data seriously. We use industry-standard encryption and secure storage practices to protect your information. Your messages and files are never accessed by our team unless necessary for troubleshooting or legal purposes.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body p-3">
                            <h2 class="card-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-gear-fill me-2"></i>Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
                            <p class="card-text">We will retain your data for as long as your account is active. If you choose to deactivate your account, we will anonymize or delete your personal information in accordance with our data retention policies.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>